text: Pablo Corral Embade (born January 25, 1972 in A Coruña) is a swimmer from Spain. He has a disability: he is blind and is an B2/S12 type swimmer. He raced at the 1996 Summer Paralympics. He finished second in the 50 meter freestyle. == References == Category:Spanish swimmers Category:Living people Category:1972 births Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Spain Category:1996 Summer Paralympics Category:Sportspeople with disabilities, type S12 Category:Sportspeople with disabilities, type B2 Category:Sportspeople from A Coruña
